title: NoSleep Podcast S5E19a - Gone
description:
We're off this week but don't want to leave you empty-handed...or with empty ears.

To show you our undying love we present the tale, "The Spider of My Love" by John Contad. We'll be back with S5E20 next week.

"The Spider of My Love" written by John Contad and read by David Cummings.


Click here to learn more about John Contad


Podcast produced by: David Cummings
